node.accessibility_caption: Miami realtor, miami real estate, move to miami, miami model

node.text:
✨ SECRETS OUT ✨
As some of you may have assumed with all the visits, I’ll be moving to Miami this September! I am super excited about this new chapter in my life and am proud to say that I officially have my real estate license in Florida 😍 can’t wait for this journey to begin and all the new experiences that come my way. Thank you for all the love and support from my friends and family ❤️
GET READY MIAMI, HERE I COME!!

#miamirealtor #miamirealestate #movetomiami
